---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import FadeIn from '../components/FadeIn.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title='협찬의의 | IMUN.FARM' description='IMUN.FARM 콘텐츠 협업, 기술 교류, 스폰서십 문의 안내'>
	<div class='min-h-screen flex flex-col lg:flex-row relative'>

		<!-- Left Column: Sticky image -->
		<div class='lg:w-1/2 relative min-h-[400px] lg:h-screen lg:sticky lg:top-0 z-0'>
			<div class='absolute inset-0'>
				<img
					src='/images/ideas-hero-bg.png'
					alt='IMUN.FARM 지식 협업'
					class='w-full h-full object-cover'
				/>
				<div class='absolute inset-0 bg-gray-950/70'></div>
				<div class='absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-950/90 via-gray-950/30 to-transparent'></div>
			</div>

			<div class='absolute bottom-10 left-10 right-10 text-white z-10'>
				<FadeIn delay={0.2} direction='up'>
					<span class='text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm block mb-4'>IMUN.FARM × 협업</span>
					<h1 class='text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-extrabold mb-4 leading-tight' style='color: white !important;'>
						지식을 함께<br />재배합니다.
					</h1>
					<p class='text-lg text-white/85 font-light max-w-md leading-relaxed'>
						콘텐츠 제안, 기술 협업, 스폰서십 — <br />어떤 형태의 연결도 환영합니다.
					</p>

					<!-- Trust signals -->
					<div class='flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8'>
						<div class='flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm'>
							<svg class='w-4 h-4 text-primary' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 20 20'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z' clip-rule='evenodd'/></svg>
							<span>3일 내 회신</span>
						</div>
						<div class='flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm'>
							<svg class='w-4 h-4 text-primary' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 20 20'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z' clip-rule='evenodd'/></svg>
							<span>장르 불문 환영</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</FadeIn>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Right Column: Scrollable content -->
		<div class='lg:w-1/2 bg-white dark:bg-[#0a0910] relative z-10'>
			<div class='max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 lg:py-32'>

				<!-- Header -->
				<FadeIn direction='up'>
					<div class='mb-16'>
						<span class='text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-2 block'>Collaboration</span>
						<h2 class='text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-text-main dark:text-white'>
							협업 및 문의 안내
						</h2>
						<p class='text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed'>
							콘텐츠 아이디어부터 기술 협업, 스폰서십까지 — <br />
							다양한 방식으로 함께할 수 있습니다.
						</p>
					</div>
				</FadeIn>

				<!-- Category Grid -->
				<div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16'>
					<FadeIn delay={0.1} class='h-full'>
						<div class='p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors h-full'>
							<div class='w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4'>
								<svg class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z'/></svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class='font-bold text-lg mb-2'>콘텐츠 제안</h3>
							<p class='text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400'>
								다뤘으면 하는 주제, 글감 아이디어를 보내주세요
							</p>
						</div>
					</FadeIn>

					<FadeIn delay={0.2} class='h-full'>
						<div class='p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors h-full'>
							<div class='w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4'>
								<svg class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4'/></svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class='font-bold text-lg mb-2'>기술 협업</h3>
							<p class='text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400'>
								오픈소스, 프로젝트, 공동 연구 등 기술 교류
							</p>
						</div>
					</FadeIn>

					<FadeIn delay={0.3} class='h-full'>
						<div class='p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors h-full'>
							<div class='w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4'>
								<svg class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z'/></svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class='font-bold text-lg mb-2'>스폰서십</h3>
							<p class='text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400'>
								IT 제품·서비스 소개 및 브랜드 협업 콘텐츠
							</p>
						</div>
					</FadeIn>

					<FadeIn delay={0.4} class='h-full'>
						<div class='p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors h-full'>
							<div class='w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4'>
								<svg class='w-6 h-6' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z'/></svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class='font-bold text-lg mb-2'>아이디어 교류</h3>
							<p class='text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400'>
								독자로서의 피드백, 아이디어 보드 외 직접 제안
							</p>
						</div>
					</FadeIn>
				</div>

				<!-- Process Steps -->
				<FadeIn direction='up'>
					<div class='relative py-10 mb-16 border-t border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800'>
						<h3 class='font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-8'>진행 과정</h3>
						<div class='flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between relative'>
							<div class='absolute top-[15px] left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 hidden md:block -z-10'></div>

							{[
								{ num: '1', label: '문의 접수' },
								{ num: '2', label: '내용 검토' },
								{ num: '3', label: '방향 협의' },
								{ num: '4', label: '협업 시작' },
							].map((step, i) => (
								<div class='flex md:flex-col items-center gap-4 md:gap-2 mb-6 md:mb-0 bg-white dark:bg-[#0a0910] md:bg-transparent pr-4 md:pr-0'>
									<div class={`w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm shadow-md ${i === 0 ? 'bg-primary text-white' : 'bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300'}`}>
										{step.num}
									</div>
									<span class='text-sm font-medium'>{step.label}</span>
								</div>
							))}
						</div>
					</div>
				</FadeIn>

				<!-- Email CTA -->
				<FadeIn direction='up'>
					<div class='bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700'>
						<div class='absolute -right-10 -top-10 w-40 h-40 bg-primary/10 dark:bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-primary/20 dark:group-hover:bg-primary/30 transition-colors'></div>
						<h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-2'>바로 연락하기</h3>
						<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 text-sm'>
							가볍게 아이디어를 던져도 좋습니다. 3일 내 회신드립니다.
						</p>
						<a
							href='mailto:denosinfo@gmail.com'
							class='block w-full text-center py-4 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02] shadow-lg shadow-primary/20'
						>
							denosinfo@gmail.com
						</a>
					</div>
				</FadeIn>

				<!-- FAQ -->
				<div class='mt-16'>
					<h3 class='font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-6'>자주 묻는 질문</h3>
					<div class='space-y-4'>
						<details class='group border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 pb-4'>
							<summary class='flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none'>
								<span>콘텐츠 협업은 어떤 방식으로 진행되나요?</span>
								<span class='transition group-open:rotate-180'>
									<svg fill='none' height='24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='1.5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' width='24'><path d='M6 9l6 6 6-6'></path></svg>
								</span>
							</summary>
							<p class='text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400 mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed'>
								제품/서비스를 직접 사용해보고 솔직한 경험을 기반으로 글을 작성합니다. 광고임을 명시하며, 사실과 다른 내용은 게재하지 않습니다.
							</p>
						</details>
						<details class='group border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 pb-4'>
							<summary class='flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none'>
								<span>콘텐츠 제안은 어떻게 하면 되나요?</span>
								<span class='transition group-open:rotate-180'>
									<svg fill='none' height='24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='1.5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' width='24'><path d='M6 9l6 6 6-6'></path></svg>
								</span>
							</summary>
							<p class='text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400 mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed'>
								이메일로 자유롭게 보내주시거나, 아이디어 페이지에서 직접 제안하실 수 있습니다. 간단한 메모 수준도 환영합니다.
							</p>
						</details>
						<details class='group border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 pb-4'>
							<summary class='flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none'>
								<span>독자로서 피드백을 보내고 싶어요</span>
								<span class='transition group-open:rotate-180'>
									<svg fill='none' height='24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='1.5' viewBox='0 0 24 24' width='24'><path d='M6 9l6 6 6-6'></path></svg>
								</span>
							</summary>
							<p class='text-text-muted dark:text-gray-400 mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed'>
								가장 환영하는 유형의 연락입니다. 오타, 오류 지적, 보완 요청 등 모두 소중하게 읽고 반영합니다.
							</p>
						</details>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
